<body><p>GE.<footnote name="1">General Assembly resolution 60/1. </footnote>4-16732  (E) 
</p>
<p>&#61482;&#61489;&#61492;&#61489;&#61494;&#61495;&#61491;&#61490;&#61482; 
</p>
<p><b>Human Rights Council 
Twenty-seventh session 
</b></p>
<p>Agenda item 3 
</p>
<p><b>Promotion and protection of all human rights, civil, 
</b></p>
<p><b>political, economic, social and cultural rights, 
</b></p>
<p><b>including the right to development 
</b></p>
<p><b>  Algeria, Armenia,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Australia,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Bahrain,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Belarus,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Belgium,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Bosnia and 
</b></p>
<p><b>Herzegovina,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Botswana, Brazil, Bulgaria,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Cameroon,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> China, Colombia,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Congo, 
</b></p>
<p><b>Costa Rica, Croatia,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Cuba, Cyprus,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Denmark,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Egypt,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> El Salvador,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Estonia, 
</b></p>
<p><b>France, Germany, Greece,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Guatemala,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Honduras,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Hungary,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Indonesia, Iraq,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> 
</b></p>
<p><b>Italy, Japan, Kuwait, Latvia,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Lebanon,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
