<p><b>Portugal,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Qatar,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Republic of Korea, Republic of Moldova,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Romania, Russian 
</b></p>
<p><b>Federation, Saudi Arabia, Senegal,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Serbia,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Slovakia,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
